title: DC New 52 Week 170
description:
This weeks DC New 52 comics.  I can't take credit for any of these, I just compiled them and uploaded since no one had done it yet this week.  If you enjoy these comics, BUY THEM and support the industry.  Print is dying media and that's a damn shame.

Included:

Action Comics 37
Aquaman and the Others 8
Batman Eternal 35
Detective Comics 37
Earth 2 Worlds End 9
Earth 2 29
Gotham Academy 3
Grayson 5
Green Arrow 37
Green Lantern 37
Justice League 3000 12
Lobo 3
Secret Six 1
Sinestro 7
Swamp Thing 37
The New 52 Futures End 31

I may have missed something here... first torrent.  Hope you enjoy
